parport0: Printer, Hewlett-Packard HP LaserJet 2100 Series
</pre>}}

对于USB打印机：

{{Cmd|lsusb|output=<pre>
(...)
Bus 001 Device 007: ID 03f0:1004 Hewlett-Packard DeskJet 970c/970cse
</pre>
